clientSide.Stubs

Class RepoStub

  • java.lang.Object
    • clientSide.Stubs.RepoStub

  • public class RepoStub
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements the Repository Stub. This file consists on the implementation of the Repository's shared region functions, but in a message approach version. In each function, a connection is established and a message is sent to the Repository Interface that will execute the proper function from the original shared region itself.
